==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Temper screw
<hw>Tem"per screw</hw>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>A screw link, to which is
attached the rope of a rope-drilling apparatus, for feeding and slightly
turning the drill jar at each stroke.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A set screw used for adjusting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tempest</ent>⟦br⟧
